text: The Swan 46 Mk II was designed by German Frers and built by Nautor's Swan and first launched in 1990. It uses the same hull as the Swan 46 Mk I but with a slightly more powerful rig and some refinements. ==External links== * Nautor Swan * German Frers Official Website ==References== Category:Sailing yachts Category:Keelboats Category:1980s sailboat type designs Category:Sailboat types built by Nautor Swan Category:Sailboat type designs by Germán Frers
